"title": "6203: mortality",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6203: mortality",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The human state of being subject to death and decay. God did not create human beings to be like this; mortality is the consequence of sin and is countered by the gospel promise of eternal life in Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Mortality originated in the fall</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>It is the decree of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:3\">PSA 90:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:5\">PSA 90:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:19\">GEN 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:3\">GEN 6:3</a></p>\n<h3>It is universal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:20\">ECC 3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:22</a></p>\n<h3>It is inevitable</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:14\">2SA 14:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:23\">JOB 30:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:2\">ECC 3:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></p>\n<h3>It is a judgment from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:15-Rom5:19\">ROM 5:15–5:19</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27\">HEB 9:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Mortality extends to the creation</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:20-Rom8:21\">ROM 8:20–8:21</a></p>\n<h3>Human beings likened to the animals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:19\">ECC 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Human beings likened to the grass</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:5-Ps90:6\">PSA 90:5–90:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:15-Ps103:16\">PSA 103:15–103:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:7\">ISA 40:6–40:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:24\">1PE 1:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:10\">JAS 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The natural reaction to mortality</h2>\n<h3>A sense of oppression</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:8-Job10:9\">JOB 10:8–10:9</a></p>\n<h3>Carefree abandon</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:32\">1CO 15:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:13\">ISA 22:13</a></p>\n<h2>The godly reaction to mortality</h2>\n<h3>Humility</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:6-Job20:11\">JOB 20:6–20:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:29\">PSA 22:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:48\">PSA 89:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:21-Eccl3:22\">ECC 3:21–3:22</a></p>\n<h3>Trust</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:25\">LUK 12:25</a></p>\n<h3>The pursuit of wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:12\">PSA 90:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Saving faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6\">ISA 55:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:4-Ps39:8\">PSA 39:4–39:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a></p>\n<h3>The struggle with sin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:12\">ROM 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:14-Rom7:25\">ROM 7:14–7:25</a></p>\n<h2>Death is not the end</h2>\n<h3>The spirit returns to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:23\">PHP 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>The body will be raised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:53-1Cor15:54\">1CO 15:53–15:54</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:8\">ISA 25:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:44\">1CO 15:42–15:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:4\">2CO 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>Eternal life through Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25-John11:26\">JHN 11:25–11:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:46\">MAT 25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9-2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11-1John5:12\">1JN 5:11–5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:3-Rev22:5\">REV 22:3–22:5</a></p>\n<h3>Eternal punishment for the wicked</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:46\">MAT 25:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:15\">REV 20:15</a></p>",
